KG name: World War 1 as Linked Open Data
Description: This dataset contains strictly quality-controlled rich information on events- actors and places related to the First World War. As such- it is meant to be used as a reference dataset to which other datasets (e.g. museum or library collections dealing with WW1 topics) can be linked.
